____________________________________________________________________________

Use this form as a date-picker from a calendar.  It is recommended
that this form be used in preference to the CnEcCalendarForm form
because of better (startup) performance, particularly for a thin-
client connection.

This form's "modalResult" value will return the following values:

	CNEC_DIALOG_SELECT	- A valid date was selected.
	CNEC_DIALOG_CANCEL	- The User cancelled the form.</text>
